# -*- mode: python; -*-
# build file for 10gen db
# this request scons
# you can get from http://www.scons.org
# then just type scons

# some common tasks
#   build 64-bit mac and pushing to s3
#      scons --64 s3dist
#      scons --distname=0.8 s3dist
#      all s3 pushes require settings.py and simples3

